</div>

<div class="col-sm-10 col-sm-offset-1 ">
	<h2>How does Cater Request work?</h2>
	<p>You create an event, select the food, select the restaurants you
		want to request the price quote and request for price quote.
		Restaurants respond with price in less than 24 hours. You have 24
		hours to make the payment and confirm the order.</p>

	<h2>How much does it cost for the Customer?</h2>
	<p>The service is completely free for customers. You pay only the
		price restaurant has quoted and in some case the delivery charge.
		There is no service charge of any kind.</p>

	<h2>How do I know my order is confirmed?</h2>
	<p>Once the restaurant gives a price quote for your request, he is
		ready to take your order given you make the payment in less than 24
		hours. Once the payment is done you get a confirmation email from
		Cater Request about the confirmation of your order..</p>

	<h2>Forgot password?</h2>
	<p>You can reset the password on clicking the "Forgot Password"
		link on Login page. You can email contact info@caterrequest.com
		customer care and describe your problem to get help.</p>

	<h2>Why register to Cater Request?</h2>
	<p>Restaurants owners are very busy. To only send serious customer
		requests to restaurants for price quote request.</p>

	<h2>How secure is your payment gateway?</h2>
	<p>We use Stripe service to process secure payments.</p>

	<h2>Do I have to use my credit card to make payments?</h2>
	<p>Yes. We use stripe secure payment gateway to process payments.
		Stripe service accepts all major credit cards.</p>

	<h2>What kind of food can I order?</h2>
	<p>We have a wide range of restaurants in our system. And we are
		actively adding more restaurants to our restaurant network. If you
		don’t see your favorite restaurant, please email us the restaurant
		details to info@caterrequest.com. We will work on bringing the
		restaurant on to our system.</p>


	<h2>Is my food always delivered?</h2>
	<p>Most of the restaurants deliver food. Very few restaurants do
		not have the capacity to deliver and some cases depending on the
		distance the restaurant may inform you about the delivery when price
		quoted for your request.</p>
	<h2>How does Cater Request work?</h2>
	<p>Cater Request is a three step simple process. You search for
		your favorite restaurant. Choose from the restaurant menu and request
		for price. Once the restaurant respond with the price quote you can
		make a payment and confirm the order. We have another feature for
		price comparison, please watch the explainer video on the homepage to
		understand the process of how Cater Request’s price comparison works
		works.</p>
	<h2>Can I place the order for today?</h2>
	<p>Orders can be placed only for events 72 hours in future.</p>
	<h2>How can I see my orders placed?</h2>
	<p>All the new requests, past orders and confirmed order can viewed
		from customer dashboard.</p>
	<h2>I just received my order, some menu items are missing. What
		should I do?</h2>
	<p>There is nothing upsetting than having not seeing your favorite
		dish. Please contact the restaurant immediately. If you don't get the
		issue resolved immediately, please contact us via email or phone. We
		are available 24 hours everyday.</p>
	<h2>Where can I find receipt for my order?</h2>
	<p>We send out payment receipt when payment is made against an
		order to the email address entered during the payment process.</p>
	<h2>Can I repeat my favorite orders?</h2>
	<p>We are working on having this feature. We will offer this
		service with the next version of Cater Request in April.</p>
	<h2>Can I change my order once it is placed?</h2>
	<p>You can change the order any time you want before you made
		payment to the order. You can change your order and request the
		restaurant to give a new price quote for the new/updated request.</p>
	<h2>Is there any fee with canceling an order?</h2>
	<p>There is no fee for canceling an order. In some cases when the
		food is already prepared, the restaurant may charge for the food
		already prepared depending on the time of the order cancellation.
		Please contact Cater Request customer service with any order
		cancellation issues.</p>
	<h2>What is the delivery charge?</h2>
	<p>Some restaurants offer free delivery service depending on the
		size of the order. Delivery charge is included in the price quote from
		the restaurant. There is no separate delivery charge.</p>
